Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,, -你好 -你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去很冷靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,, -很緊張 -緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:00:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有在攝像機前聊過天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,總之儘力回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,首先名字年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,還有平時做什麼 請告知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好的我是由奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,年齡是29歲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,現在工作是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拍自然寫真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,, -看不出是29歲 -真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,29歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去更年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,, -然後是自然照片嗎 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,以前經常旅遊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去過各國
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,會拍動物 還有自然照片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這個也能是工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,去過什麼國家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,去過的 現在能想起的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,衣索比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,馬達加斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還有肯亞泰國印度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然都知道名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是具體也不知道在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,, -是去拍自然照片嗎 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想拍那邊的動物的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼對這些有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不拍人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也拍過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是感覺拍動物和風景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我更充實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,, -現在在日本\N -是的現在在日本上班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在IT類公司上班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這個和自然照片有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,, -沒有嗎 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,, -有一點微妙的聯繫嗎\N -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,, -是有那樣的 -原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 挺一般的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,, -是呢 要錢吧 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,會在當地工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只是拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拍照片 是有學過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,學生時代學過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,然後畢業同時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,去了個憧憬的寫真館
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,, -因此嗎 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺很跟著興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,, -一樣的 -是說務必出版嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,然後同意就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看了自己的作品傳達熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,最開始就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,, -那不容易呢 -不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,, -真的感覺之前很破碎\N -是的 沒什麼自信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒自信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺沒什麼藝術天分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是能被隨意揉胸部的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不會揉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是會摸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,, -真的嗎 -因為是男權社會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很多下流笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那會說什麼脫了站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,, -看看膚色什麼的\N -果然有這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,會有開玩笑的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不會拍自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,, -自己嗎 -自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不會想拍自己的身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,今天會看的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,出演動機是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,動機是那個我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只和外國人做過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有點興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以想拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好直接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,, -那第一次做愛不在日本嗎\N -很遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,都超過20歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,, -初體驗是和外國人 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是和什麼國家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,肯亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,肯亞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就那樣主動邀請你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎確實會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,, -不會這樣嗎 -會的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,, -但是和不少外國人做了\N -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,作為經驗 和很多國家的做過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼國家的人好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然沒有日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼國家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都沒什麼前戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,直接就進去了 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以想體驗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,, -看過日本AV嗎 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以感覺和平時的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,做愛舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然估計很多沒經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是什麼最舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,忍住高潮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,會高潮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼讓你高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,, -肉棒 -肉棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,用肉棒摩擦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,還是插入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,插入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,, -插入很舒服嗎 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,, -什麼樣的肉棒最舒服\N -什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,硬的 軟的 長的 短的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,粗細
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,, -很多呢 -很多種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,, -硬的 -硬的更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,, -能插入多深的 -深一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,, -那腿伸直 -什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,聊這種話題交叉腿的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,說是不夾住會有什麼出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,腿伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,, -繼續 -繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,自己摸 肉棒頂著哪舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,用右手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,, -裙子拉長 -好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是想進行不是馬上插入的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,盯著看如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,會害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一直盯著看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,現在看著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在想像衣服下是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡以外的敏感帶是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好像沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起下巴給我看看脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拉長脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,敏感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼敏感的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不說也能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是擅自想像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是應該有大肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,會這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,, -但是大肉棒插入過你吧 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,全身都要被舔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,算是頂尖的舔肉棒的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,比如有想被摸的地方的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,, -摸我這裡 -什麼這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡嗎好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好濕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,, -好厲害 -怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你說插入很快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是你自己要求的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好濕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,被拍的人會想像得出吧
